-- SBI to Create Investment Funds With Jefferies Group for U.S., Asia Stocks
-- Go Onomitsu
-- 2010-06-29T00:19:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/sbi-to-create-investment-funds-with-jefferies-group-for-u-s-asia-stocks.html

          
          
             SBI Holdings Inc., a Japanese
financial services firm, will create two funds with New York-
based Jefferies Group Inc. to invest in U.S. and Asian
companies. SBI made the announcement in a press release
distributed through the Tokyo Stock Exchange.   
 To contact the reporter on this story:
Go Onomitsu in Tokyo at 
 gonomitsu@bloomberg.net   
          
          


  


        